{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- then, while I was working in the plant one day-- I also worked for the couple in the-- in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would do his dishes and prepare his food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had-- he would have his buddies come in and play cards, because they-- they had-- they had an easy life in-- inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They stayed home all-- like, in the barracks all day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They slept up-- slept through the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, when it came at night, they were awake, and everybody else went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was-- I liked the job, because it was giving me extra food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I was preparing food for them, I made sure that there was enough that they-- was left over for me and my father that I gave him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a very-- but what it-- the-- the difficulty was that I was very tired, because I stayed up till, maybe, 11 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at 5 o'clock, I had to get up with the appel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so, during the day, I tried to find a place where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the warehouse was not very busy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was two of us working in the warehouse, so I would tell the other guy that was working with me is, I'm going to go and sleep.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a desk-- just a small desk with a front-- roll-up front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would go inside, put my legs in, and pull myself in, close the desk up, so that nobody could see me sleeping, even when they-- because the-- the warehouse was wire mesh.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So no matter where you were, if you were sitting and sleeping, somebody could see you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you-- you're looking for a beating.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
